01:45:37.000 --> 01:45:45.000
I just never talked to, I don't know why it's a North Turkdom. I don't have anything against them. I just never talked to them. You know, I mean, this is the way he was.

01:45:45.000 --> 01:45:52.000
But that's the reason we got that apartment. And so I got that apartment, we got that apartment because of those Irish nuns.

01:45:52.000 --> 01:46:02.000
Because I said, I said, when he's broken his broken, it was very distant. I said, she's, I haven't heard that music to my ears. And I so startled her to hear me say that.

