And besides, because of the new world picture, you got a sand cart in the cooking drawer stealing us, not my problem. Well, that's sort of like center over the top. That's Friday night Saturday night. I got another call this time. The voice is sacramentally sweet.

01:57:59.000 --> 01:58:15.000
Mr. Jones, yes, my name is Dora McDonald. You know, Mr. Jones, Dr. King, and joined so much is visited with you and Mrs. Jones, but you know, Mr. Jones, he forgot to invite you to be his guest at a church tomorrow.

