But I can interpret his body of work. And I can interpret what I think he would say. And I think he would come down on what I said earlier, whether people would say, well, homosexuality is a sin, so what I think Martin could be on any such.

02:42:29.000 --> 02:42:49.000
It's not about all the things you object to. It's about an elementary thing called love and compassion. Remember the principle, founding injunction of his Christianity was love, that's what it was founded on. Love, the enemy.

